{
  "video_id": "GPsZfw9ADkY",
  "title": "How Bugs Are Trained For TV And Movies | Movies Insider",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1100.0,
      "end_time": 2540.0,
      "text": "- [Announcer] Some of the biggest stars in Hollywood"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2540.0,
      "end_time": 5850.0,
      "text": "are some of the smallest creatures on the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 5850.0,
      "end_time": 10120.0,
      "text": "Real live insects like spiders, locusts, and butterflies"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 10120.0,
      "end_time": 13459.0,
      "text": "play crucial roles in many memorable blockbuster films."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13460.0,
      "end_time": 16490.0,
      "text": "But getting them to perform on camera is no easy task."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 16490.0,
      "end_time": 19380.0,
      "text": "- Rosie, lift up your leg. This leg."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19380.0,
      "end_time": 20250.0,
      "text": "Come on."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 20250.0,
      "end_time": 22400.0,
      "text": "Oh see, she did this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 22400.0,
      "end_time": 23669.0,
      "text": "Oh, there she goes."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 23670.0,
      "end_time": 26470.0,
      "text": "And that's just a little trick of putting a little pressure"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 26470.0,
      "end_time": 29619.0,
      "text": "on her back leg that causes her front leg to come up."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 29620.0,
      "end_time": 30870.0,
      "text": "- [Announcer] That's Steven Kutcher."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 30870.0,
      "end_time": 33290.0,
      "text": "He's an entomologist and the go to guy"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 33290.0,
      "end_time": 35310.0,
      "text": "for all things bugs in Hollywood."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 35310.0,
      "end_time": 38470.0,
      "text": "He's worked with a variety of insects on over 100 films"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 38470.0,
      "end_time": 42240.0,
      "text": "in his career including \"Arachnophobia,\" \"Jurassic Park,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 42240.0,
      "end_time": 43390.0,
      "text": "and \"Spider-Man.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 43390.0,
      "end_time": 47130.0,
      "text": "- Understanding insect behavior is really the key."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 47130.0,
      "end_time": 49670.0,
      "text": "It's not training them because you don't have time"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 49670.0,
      "end_time": 51795.0,
      "text": "to train them in the film industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 51795.0,
      "end_time": 55160.0,
      "text": "When you work with insects, you wanna corral the insects."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 55160.0,
      "end_time": 57569.0,
      "text": "You wanna be able to control them."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 57570.0,
      "end_time": 59310.0,
      "text": "- [Announcer] He's used a number of different techniques"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 59310.0,
      "end_time": 61510.0,
      "text": "to get the bugs to move in the right direction"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 61510.0,
      "end_time": 64860.0,
      "text": "involving lights, air, and temperature."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 64860.0,
      "end_time": 66800.0,
      "text": "- Let's say you're a bug."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 66800.0,
      "end_time": 68920.0,
      "text": "How can I make you move?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 68920.0,
      "end_time": 73920.0,
      "text": "Well, I could blow air at you, like 60 miles an hour air."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 74270.0,
      "end_time": 75899.0,
      "text": "You're going to move."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 75900.0,
      "end_time": 78470.0,
      "text": "I could light a little fire under you"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 78470.0,
      "end_time": 81500.0,
      "text": "or set you on something that's really hot."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 81500.0,
      "end_time": 84340.0,
      "text": "You're gonna get up out of your seat and move."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 84340.0,
      "end_time": 86710.0,
      "text": "I could chill down the room."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 86710.0,
      "end_time": 88619.0,
      "text": "- [Announcer] For example, let's take a look"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 88620.0,
      "end_time": 91500.0,
      "text": "at one of the most famous and terrifying spider films"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 91500.0,
      "end_time": 93980.0,
      "text": "of all time, \"Arachnophobia.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 93980.0,
      "end_time": 98330.0,
      "text": "- The great thing about that film was it was before CGI."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 98330.0,
      "end_time": 102500.0,
      "text": "So we had to do everything real except for one shot."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 102500.0,
      "end_time": 104860.0,
      "text": "- [Announcer] He devised a clever yet simple rig"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 104860.0,
      "end_time": 107170.0,
      "text": "to get all the spiders where they needed to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 107170.0,
      "end_time": 110377.0,
      "text": "- They would say, \"We want a spider to crawl into a slipper"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 110377.0,
      "end_time": 111660.0,
      "text": "\"from four feet away.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 111660.0,
      "end_time": 116229.0,
      "text": "So I came up with this idea of invisible vibrating wires."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 116230.0,
      "end_time": 118700.0,
      "text": "Chance of vibrating wires that you couldn't see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 118700.0,
      "end_time": 120200.0,
      "text": "the camera couldn't see."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 120200.0,
      "end_time": 122870.0,
      "text": "But I could make the spider go directly to the spot"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 122870.0,
      "end_time": 124470.0,
      "text": "I wanted it to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 124470.0,
      "end_time": 126200.0,
      "text": "- [Announcer] Kutcher's first big Hollywood gig"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 126200.0,
      "end_time": 128780.0,
      "text": "was on the \"Exorcist II\" and it involved working with"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 128780.0,
      "end_time": 130890.0,
      "text": "three thousand live locusts."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 130889.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134790.0,
      "text": "- There's a scene where James Earl Jones has to look"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 134800.0,
      "end_time": 137400.0,
      "text": "at a cage of locusts and the locusts were all on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 137400.0,
      "end_time": 141800.0,
      "text": "But how do you move hundreds of locusts up on the screen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 141800.0,
      "end_time": 145377.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Get a light, a studio light that gives off heat"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 145377.0,
      "end_time": 148347.0,
      "text": "\"and shining against the side of the cage.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 149317.0,
      "end_time": 152110.0,
      "text": "And they did and all the locusts moved up onto the cage"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 152110.0,
      "end_time": 153600.0,
      "text": "to be near the heat."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 153600.0,
      "end_time": 155230.0,
      "text": "Then they took the light away."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 155230.0,
      "end_time": 156549.0,
      "text": "- [Announcer] In \"Jurassic Park,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 156550.0,
      "end_time": 157910.0,
      "text": "Kutcher was the man responsible"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 157910.0,
      "end_time": 160450.0,
      "text": "for the iconic dead mosquitoes in amber."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 160450.0,
      "end_time": 162428.0,
      "text": "- So it's supposed to be a mosquito."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 162428.0,
      "end_time": 165150.0,
      "text": "First, it's really a crane fly."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 165150.0,
      "end_time": 169760.0,
      "text": "And I put antenna from another insect on the crane fly."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 169760.0,
      "end_time": 173910.0,
      "text": "I took a bent insect pin and made it for its mouth part."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 173910.0,
      "end_time": 175630.0,
      "text": "I created the wings."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 175630.0,
      "end_time": 177299.0,
      "text": "- [Announcer] And he worked with a live mosquito"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 177300.0,
      "end_time": 179350.0,
      "text": "in the DNA Explainer video."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 179350.0,
      "end_time": 181630.0,
      "text": "- So I would chill the mosquito down"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 181630.0,
      "end_time": 183320.0,
      "text": "so that it wouldn't move."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 183320.0,
      "end_time": 185590.0,
      "text": "And then I would drip honey on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 185590.0,
      "end_time": 188633.0,
      "text": "And then it got tumbled down with the honey."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 189550.0,
      "end_time": 191680.0,
      "text": "- [Announcer] In the 2002 movie \"Spider-Man,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 191680.0,
      "end_time": 194150.0,
      "text": "there's a scene where Peter Parker first gets bitten."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 194150.0,
      "end_time": 196880.0,
      "text": "Kutcher was actually above Toby McGuire with a paint brush."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 196880.0,
      "end_time": 199370.0,
      "text": "- And what the spider will do is it will crawl"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 199370.0,
      "end_time": 201995.0,
      "text": "along the edge until it reaches this part"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 201995.0,
      "end_time": 203880.0,
      "text": "and then it will hang on."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 203880.0,
      "end_time": 206810.0,
      "text": "And I would just tap it like this which would cause"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 206810.0,
      "end_time": 208770.0,
      "text": "the spider to web down."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 208770.0,
      "end_time": 210650.0,
      "text": "- [Announcer] While he says he rarely ever gets bitten"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 210650.0,
      "end_time": 212930.0,
      "text": "or stung, he takes precautions"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 212930.0,
      "end_time": 214600.0,
      "text": "to protect the other human actors."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 214600.0,
      "end_time": 218340.0,
      "text": "In \"Roadhouse 66,\" Judge Reinhold is driving a car"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 218340.0,
      "end_time": 220840.0,
      "text": "and I had to have a scorpion crawl over his shoulder."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 220840.0,
      "end_time": 223200.0,
      "text": "So I put a little cap on the scorpion's stinger"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 223200.0,
      "end_time": 225803.0,
      "text": "that looked like the stinger so it wouldn't hurt him."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 225803.0,
      "end_time": 226880.0,
      "text": "- [Announcer] And there's also a rule on set"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 226880.0,
      "end_time": 229250.0,
      "text": "that no bugs are hurt during production."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 229250.0,
      "end_time": 232370.0,
      "text": "- In making of a movie, you can't harm a cockroach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 232370.0,
      "end_time": 234240.0,
      "text": "or a fly, or a maggot."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 234240.0,
      "end_time": 237920.0,
      "text": "But if the fly flies to craft service, you can swat it."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 237920.0,
      "end_time": 240409.0,
      "text": "- [Announcer] He can get some of his bugs from pet suppliers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 240470.0,
      "end_time": 242620.0,
      "text": "but most he goes out and collects himself."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 242620.0,
      "end_time": 245740.0,
      "text": "And Kutcher's home is also full of bugs, by choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 245740.0,
      "end_time": 250740.0,
      "text": "- Right now, I have mosquitoes, crane flies, caterpillars"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 251850.0,
      "end_time": 253440.0,
      "text": "in my refrigerator."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 253440.0,
      "end_time": 256620.0,
      "text": "The world is filled with people who do not like insects"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 256620.0,
      "end_time": 259920.0,
      "text": "which is a great opportunity to teach those people"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 259920.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263550.0,
      "text": "the joys and wonders of all of the arthropods in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 263550.0,
      "end_time": 265370.0,
      "text": "and how you can relate to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 265370.0,
      "end_time": 267627.0,
      "text": "And when you understand how they work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 267627.0,
      "end_time": 270242.0,
      "text": "the world is a better place."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 271890.0,
      "end_time": 275580.0,
      "text": "- To make the spider go, I just tap her back legs."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 275581.0,
      "end_time": 278503.0,
      "text": "And this gets her to crawl up."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 279540.0,
      "end_time": 281640.0,
      "text": "To make her stop, I cover her eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 281640.0,
      "end_time": 282950.0,
      "text": "She has eight eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 282950.0,
      "end_time": 284923.0,
      "text": "She's just looking for a dark place."
    }
  ]
}